PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FITV News' Louisa Britton spoke to
OL,8,Fformer ketamine users from Dorset
OL,9,Fabout their experiences with the drug.
OL,11,FFormer ketamine users from Dorset have
OL,12,Fspoken of the destructive effects of
OL,13,Fthe drug, as figures show the number
OL,14,Fof people seeking help has risen
OL,15,Fsharply in recent years.
OL,17,FLiv from Bridport in Dorset first took
OL,18,Fdrugs aged 11 but it wasn't until she
OL,19,Fwas at university that she was
OL,20,Fintroduced to ketamine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FShe says it was easy and cheap to
OL,8,Faccess and quickly took a hold of her
OL,9,Flife. The impacts were both physical
OL,10,Fand mental and led her to be admitted
OL,11,Fto hospital several times.
OL,13,FLiv said: "I just felt very much out
OL,14,Fof reality. I would lose time and not
OL,15,Fknow why. And quite quickly it had an
OL,16,Feffect on my bladder. It led me to a
OL,17,Fvery dark place.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,F"It just kind of spiralled and got
OL,8,Fworse and worse and worse, until I was
OL,9,Fin and out of hospital every other
OL,10,Fweek for seizures, overdoses.
OL,12,F"But then I was in such a dark place
OL,13,Fthat I tried to take my own life quite
OL,14,Fseriously and ended up in a coma, on
OL,15,Flife support for a couple of days and,
OL,16,FI'm extremely grateful and lucky to
OL,17,Fhave survived that.
OL,19,F"That was the first time in my whole
OL,20,Flife I woke up and was actually like
OL,21,FI'm grateful to be alive."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FLiv has been able to access support
OL,8,Fand is now part of a campaign called
OL,9,F'Forget the Ket' which aims to raise
OL,10,Fawareness of the dangers of the drug,
OL,11,Fparticularly among young people.
OL,13,FShe met her friend Leon in recovery
OL,14,Fand they have both been clean for more
OL,15,Fthan two years.
OL,17,FHe says there are barriers to
OL,18,Faccessing support, including a lack of
OL,19,Funderstanding around how to treat drug
OL,20,Fusers and addicts.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FHe said: "The way it destroys your
OL,8,Flife and your motivation and the lives
OL,9,Fof those around you.
OL,11,F"Stigma keeps you keeps you locked
OL,12,Faway. It keeps you in your room, on
OL,13,Fyour own, in the same spiral. If more
OL,14,Fpeople understand, then the problem
OL,15,Fwill be greatly reduced."
OL,17,FKetamine is a Class B drug and is a
OL,18,Fpowerful anaesthetic that can cause
OL,19,Fserious harm, especially when used
OL,20,Fregularly or mixed with other
OL,21,Fsubstances.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
