PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FThere is no safe level of recreational
OL,8,Fketamine use, and the risks increase
OL,9,Fwith frequency and dosage.
OL,11,FIn Dorset, the number of people
OL,12,Fseeking support for ketamine use has
OL,13,Fincreased four-fold over the last
OL,14,Fthree years.
OL,16,FIn 2022, 59 people were referred for
OL,17,Ftreatment, while in 2025 that number
OL,18,Frose to 263.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FNationally the number of people
OL,8,Fstarting treatment for ketamine
OL,9,Faddiction in 2023-2024 reached 3,609
OL,10,Fin the UK, more than eight times
OL,11,Fhigher than in 2014-2015.
OL,13,FThe REACH hub in Weymouth is one of
OL,14,Fseveral drug and alcohol
OL,15,Frehabilitation centres in Dorset.
OL,16,FStaff say the number of people coming
OL,17,Fthrough its doors has gone up.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
