SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FBeth Davies, area manager at REACH
OL,8,FServices, said: "You can get a gram of
OL,9,Fketamine, which is a significant
OL,10,Famount from #15 to #30.
OL,12,F"Because ketamine is cheap to buy more
OL,13,Fpeople are using ketamine as opposed
OL,14,Fto other drugs that they might have
OL,15,Fbeen able to afford to use ten years
OL,16,Fago.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,F"It's pretty outstanding how damaging
OL,8,Fketamine is, not to minimise the harm
OL,9,Fof all the other drugs, but the trips
OL,10,Fto A&E, the bladder stretches, the
OL,11,Fscarring on internal organs, all these
OL,12,Ftypes of things.
OL,14,F"I can't think of any other drug,
OL,15,Fother than accidental poisoning and
OL,16,Fdrinking bleaches and poisons, we're
OL,17,Fused to treating in a substance misuse
OL,18,Fservice that have that much damage on
OL,19,Fthe body."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FShe added: "One of the things that
OL,8,Fstands out about ketamine in
OL,9,Fparticular, is that there are
OL,10,Fmisconceptions about the safety.
OL,12,F"I think that maybe, in the minds of
OL,13,Fyounger people in particular, they
OL,14,Fthink that's something that doesn't
OL,15,Fcost very much and that their peers
OL,16,Fhave been able to access and get hold
OL,17,Fof, will have less harm on their body.
OL,18,FThat definitely is not true.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,F"The harm on the body happens very
OL,8,Fquickly in a very short time. If you
OL,9,Fuse it at 16, within six months and
OL,10,Fyou're using it regularly, you could
OL,11,Fbe having bladder treatment in
OL,12,Fhospitals indefinitely. It will be
OL,13,Fwith you forever.
OL,15,FThe hub offers a range of support
OL,16,Fwhich Kate Taylor says she has
OL,17,Fbenefitted from after using ketamine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FKate said: "It's made a huge
OL,8,Fdifference to my life. I'm much
OL,9,Fbetter. I'm more active, I socialise
OL,10,Fnow, I know who I am. At the beginning
OL,11,FI just didn't know who I was.
OL,13,F"It's a dangerous drug to be honest.
OL,14,FAnd I think there should be more done
OL,15,Fabout it and more awareness over it as
OL,16,Fwell."
OL,18,FKay Wilson-White, from Public Health
OL,19,Fat Dorset Council, said ketamine poses
OL,20,Fparticular risks when mixed with other
OL,21,Fsubstances.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FShe said: "We have seen ketamine mixed
OL,8,Fwith synthetic opioids and overdoses
OL,9,Fbecause of that. So part of our
OL,10,Fcampaign is about raising awareness
OL,11,Fthat when you think you're buying
OL,12,Fketamine, you might actually not.
OL,14,F"You might be buying a drug that's
OL,15,Fmixed with lots of other very harmful
OL,16,Fdrugs, too. So we need to raise
OL,17,Fawareness of that.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,F"The advice is very much get help. The
OL,8,Fsupport is there for you. You will not
OL,9,Fbe judged. Even if you need to go into
OL,10,Fthe NHS or any of the providers, they
OL,11,Fare all educated and knowledgeable now
OL,12,Fabout the, harmful aspects of ketamine.
OL,14,F"It's really important that we support
OL,15,Fyou as to where you are at this point."
OL,17,FThe government recently reviewed
OL,18,Fwhether ketamine, which is currently a
OL,19,FClass B drug, should become a Class A
OL,20,Fdrug.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FThose in support of the idea say it
OL,8,Fwould better represent the dangers of
OL,9,Fthe drug.
OL,11,FThe government asked the Advisory
OL,12,FCouncil on the Misuse of Drugs (ACMD)
OL,13,Fto review the harms of ketamine misuse.
OL,15,FIn January 2026, the ACMD advised the
OL,16,Fgovernment that ketamine, "should
OL,17,Fremain a class B controlled substance,
OL,18,Fbut that police forces and health care
OL,19,Fprofessionals must receive greater
OL,20,Fsupport to better identify, prevent
OL,21,Fand respond to ketaminerelated harms".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1776503137
OL,3,C'It led me to a dark place': Former
OL,4,Cketamine user warns of dangers of the
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FIf you or anyone you know has been
OL,8,Faffected by issues mentioned in this
OL,9,Freport, support is available.
OL,11,FThe REACH service offers free and
OL,12,Fconfidential support for anyone
OL,13,Fstruggling with, or worried about,
OL,14,Fsomeone's drug or alcohol use.
OL,16,FThey are contactable on 0800 043 4656
OL,17,For by visiting waythrough.org.uk/reach.
OL,19,FOther support is also available here.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
